'''Cunto''' sidoo kale loo yaqaano '''Raashin''' ([[ingiriis]]: Food) waa shay kasta oo la quuto si looga helo nafaqo iyo [[awood]] [[jidh]]ka [[noole|nooluhu]] u baahan yahay si uu u sii noolado. 

Sida badan, cuntada waxaa laga helaa khayraadka dabiiciga ah ee [[Qolof dhul|oogada dhulka]], taas oo inta ugu badan ka timaada midhaha iyo xubnaha kala duwan ee [[dhir]]ta. Sidoo kale, cuntada waxaa keenaa [[noole|jidhka noole]] kale. 

Cuntada laga helo [[dhir]]ta iyo [[xayawaan]]ka waxay ka kooban tahay nafaqo, sida dux, fiitamiino, kaarboonhaydaraytis, borotiin iyo [[macdan]]o kala duwan oo jidhu u baahan yahay. 

Cuntada waxaa laga qaataa [[af]]ka, waxay sii dhexmarkaa hunguriga ama dhuunta ilaa [[calool|caloosha]] oo burburisa eey ka gaadho, ka dib ku darta qulqulka [[dhiig]]a oo gaadhsiiya [[unug]]yada jidhka. 

Sida [[taariikh]]du xustay, [[wakhti|wakhtiyadii hore]] [[dad]]ku waxay cuntada ku heli jireen [[ugaadhsi]] iyo [[qadhaabsi]], [[maanta]]se waxaa taas [[sadex|sadexeeysay]] waa wax-beerasho. 

Amniga iyo [[caafimaad]]ka cuntada waxaa dabagal ku sameeya hay'adaha eey ka mid yihiin International ''Association for Food Protection'', ''World Resources Institute'', ''World Food Programme'', ''Food and Agriculture Organization'', iyo ''International Food Information Council'', kuwaas oo wax ka sheega helitaanka cuntada, nafaqada cuntada, noocyada cuntada, koritaanka bulshooyinka, dhaqaalaha & cuntada iyo helitaanka [[biyo|biyaha]].
 
